{"id": "1501136461280444527", "channel_id": "1500929926704926840", "type": 0, "author_id": "364412673275723779", "author_name": "zier.0", "author_bot": false, "content": "intended/expected or not, i think it's quite misleading", "timestamp": "2026-05-05T08:20:22.136000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1500929926704926840", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Small Aliemus bug with Xu's Enlighten 3 'Doubles the next \"Resonance\" effect'", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1501136574132387870", "channel_id": "1500929926704926840", "type": 0, "author_id": "364412673275723779", "author_name": "zier.0", "author_bot": false, "content": "you would expect the 17 displayed bonus to be doubled with e3, but it isn't", "timestamp": "2026-05-05T08:20:49.042000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1500929926704926840", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Small Aliemus bug with Xu's Enlighten 3 'Doubles the next \"Resonance\" effect'", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1501137592828035203", "channel_id": "1500929926704926840", "type": 0, "author_id": "364412673275723779", "author_name": "zier.0", "author_bot": false, "content": "the displayed number is calculated separately from the actual calculations done...", "timestamp": "2026-05-05T08:24:51.918000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1500929926704926840", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Small Aliemus bug with Xu's Enlighten 3 'Doubles the next \"Resonance\" effect'", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1501138851605909545", "channel_id": "1500929926704926840", "type": 0, "author_id": "364412673275723779", "author_name": "zier.0", "author_bot": false, "content": "everything in play here for the resonance is:\n15 aliemus gain, incalc aliemus%+, xu e3\n\nIn display, we have both the aliemus gain and aliemus%+, which displays as 17 Aliemus. We only have xu e3 left, so it would be reasonable to assume that it is applied after both of those effects have already been calculated:\n`15 Aliemus Gain -> Aliemus%+ Gain -> Xu E3`\n\nHowever, in the actual Aliemus calculations, it is applied as such:\n`15 Aliemus Gain -> Xu E3 -> Aliemus%+ Gain`\n\nThe only thing that makes this an issue is the fact that the game rounds its values up which is what makes the former give 34 Aliemus in theory but what we get in the latter is 33 Aliemus", "timestamp": "2026-05-05T08:29:52.034000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-05T08:35:14.895000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "bow", "emoji_id": "1356053037159944473", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "🩷", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1500929926704926840", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Small Aliemus bug with Xu's Enlighten 3 'Doubles the next \"Resonance\" effect'", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1501139150638678096", "channel_id": "1500929926704926840", "type": 0, "author_id": "364412673275723779", "author_name": "zier.0", "author_bot": false, "content": "What's being shown to the player and what is actually happening is not the same, which is the main issue here TT", "timestamp": "2026-05-05T08:31:03.329000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1500929926704926840", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Small Aliemus bug with Xu's Enlighten 3 'Doubles the next \"Resonance\" effect'", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1501217851963473932", "channel_id": "1500929926704926840", "type": 0, "author_id": "298140360603992066", "author_name": "exo_2360", "author_bot": false, "content": "a good solution would be to update cards descriptions to reflect Xu's E3 being active, doing that will also help increase clarity overall.", "timestamp": "2026-05-05T13:43:47.187000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1500929926704926840", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Small Aliemus bug with Xu's Enlighten 3 'Doubles the next \"Resonance\" effect'", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
